text: Francesca Chircop (born 20 October 1993) is a Maltese footballer who plays as a forward for Mġarr United FC. She has been a member of the Malta women's national team. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Maltese women's footballers Category:Malta women's international footballers Category:Hibernians F.C. players
